All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Note
Represents a basic note with title, description, text, author, creation date, deadline and versioning functionality.
NoteAppGUI
Main GUI class for the Note Management System providing user interface for creating, viewing, editing and managing notes.
NoteException
Base exception class for all note-related exceptions in the Note Management System.
ProgrammingNote
Represents a programming note with programming language and coding snippet fields.
Reversable
Reverses a specific note to a previous version
TestingNote
Represents a testing note with test case, test status, and mandatory test option fields.
TestingNote.TestStatus
Enumeration representing the possible statuses for a test case execution.
TitleLengthExceededException
Exception thrown when a note title exceeds the maximum allowed length.
Versionable
Changes the current note version to the next newest version
